{"tid":2093840,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"女人返工一定要用名牌人地先睇得起你，尤其係要刺激d八婆女上司","createTime":"2020-07-04T06:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T08:56:39.000Z","uid":360601,"like":6,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"362ba827a039f5542120db24cf16e51bf497f0bd","tid":2093840,"uid":360601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:43:00.000Z","msg":"7.1大遊行，幾百個香港人比人拉左，都唔知要入監幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為一個土生土長既香港人，見依家香港亂成咁真係好心痛，呢度已經唔再係我熟悉既香港，點解我既家鄉會變成一個臭港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到咁多人被捕，我雖然好唔開心，但為左香港回歸我地偉大同埋經濟發展咁厲害既祖國23年，我都係感到非常欣慰，唔洗再做英國人隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我去左間名店買左個新手袋同銀包比自己慶祝同鼓勵自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實依家d名牌真係好平好抵，買兩樣野加埋都只係兩萬五左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好濕水，求其跌左都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7oMGv9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7oMGv9p.png&h=4b91f56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禮拜五返工咩左呢個新袋，加埋杯venti size starbucks串串貢咁行入office，我個八婆上司好酸咁講左句，新袋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我就話 係啊 男朋友送架，話係7.1禮物，我話唔洗佢係都要送，話我個袋太舊喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條傻西好似好妒忌咁話追求呢d野不如係事業上再努力d啦，男人終究係信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條八婆日日少少事就屌我，老公又係個窮撚，成日壓榨我呢d靚女下屬，之後用既袋咪又係cheap野咩michael kors<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係笑死人<br />\n<br />\n我就隨時唔開心都可以唔撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />工字不出頭啊懵炳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1377a6650e2125c60f60fa94e3ff959e7df39f","tid":2093840,"uid":140538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:46:11.000Z","msg":"呢個樓豬成日開膠post<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3d23f64282d36a60c6c743813d014e898c8d027b","tid":2093840,"uid":228955,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"個袋好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"513392bdb0a33ad8e39a33b11b6a5993d7938f12","tid":2093840,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老味坐監手足冇錢打官司<br />\n<br />\n你就買嗰25,000嘅袋上嚟曬命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 